Package com.centroid.slassessment.controller

Class CensusPolygonController

java.lang.Object
com.centroid.slassessment.controller.CensusPolygonController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/api/") public class CensusPolygonController extends Object
Controller class that specifies public APIs. Use /api/ and build function using pip or propArea for point in poly or proportionate area calculations respectively, Sum or Avg to calculate either the sum or average or the field, Inc or Pop to indicate which field to calculate on.
